videos.description: Dylan Smith drives and misses, but Deandre Ayton cleans up the play with a follow-up slam.
videos.headline: Arizona's Ayton is a man amongst boys

videos.description: Dylan Smith squeezes a pass between two defenders and Deandre Ayton lays it in for the and-1 bucket.
videos.headline: Ayton is a man's man out there

videos.description: Rawle Alkins dials up from distance and hits three 3-pointers.
videos.headline: Wildcats' Alkins feeling it from deep

videos.description: Deandre Ayton goes around a back screen and Parker Jackson-Cartwright finds him for a nasty alley-oop slam.
videos.headline: Ayton is dunking on anyone in his way

videos.description: Dylan Smith finds Deandre Ayton for the alley-oop slam then Ayton ends up wide-open a few possessions later for another dunk.
videos.headline: Ayton is a force to be reckoned with
